Name: Snowtrooper
Description:
Official Marketing Text:

The world of POP! is getting bigger—and smaller—with Bitty POP! collectibles! Expand your Star Wars™ collection with this exclusive assortment of Bitty POP! collectibles featuring some of your favourite characters from Star Wars: The Empire Strikes Back™! Each Bitty POP! comes in mystery packaging and includes one collectible figure. Who will you find? There's Bitty POP! Luke Skywalker™ (Hoth™) (1/32), Bitty POP! R2-D2™ (1/16), Bitty POP! Chewbacca™ (3/32), Bitty POP! Princess Leia™ (1/8), Bitty POP! Snowtrooper™ Gold (1/32), Bitty POP! Boba Fett™ (3/32), Bitty POP! Han Solo™ (3/32), Bitty POP! Wampa™ (1/16), Bitty POP! Dagobah Yoda™ (3/32), Bitty POP! Darth Vader™ (1/8), Bitty POP! Lando Calrissian™ (1/16), and Bitty POP! Luke Skywalker™ and Yoda™ (1/8).

Bitty POP! collectibles are packaged in hard acrylic cases with detachable bottom lids. Detachable bottom lids double as acrylic bases, to which the Bitty POP! collectibles are adhered. Vinyl collectibles are approximately 0.9 in (2.3 cm) tall. One collectible per single package purchase.

Name: Jumbo Chan Scorpion
Description:
Official Marketing Text:

Born of Funko’s reverence and passion for retro Japanese toys, Jumbo Chan is designed to emulate the charm and vibrance of iconic characters that have inspired so many of our artists. This new collection merges feel-good nostalgia and sleek stylization of beloved licenses from the ‘60s, ‘70s, and ‘80s.   

Jumbo Chan collectibles feature exuberant expressions and vibrant colors as an ode to the original art, design, and stories of each character. The packaging features bold lettering, burst icons, and full front-panel art.

Jumbo Chan Scorpion has scaled to new heights as this premium vinyl collectible, making a larger-than-life statement piece for your Mortal Kombat collection.

Collectible Details:   

  • Limited edition, only 1,200 produced.   

  • 14-inch-tall collectible.   

  • Material: hard vinyl.   

  • Includes a certificate of authenticity.   

  • Collector’s box with eye-catching, full front-panel art.

Patent faux leather, embroidery, and embossed details bring the whole look together.

Perfect for any Hello Kitty fan that wants an unforgettable piece to show off what they love.
 

Features:

  • Faux leather (polyurethane) with PVC trim
  • Sturdy top handle

  • Applique, embossed, embroidered, patent faux leather, and printed details
  • Coordinating interior lining

Collectible Details:   

  • Limited edition, only 1,200 produced.

Name: Tanjiro Kamado
Description:
Official Marketing Text:

Behold! The new premiere POP! figure, designed to be the front and center, top-shelf collectible, the Die-cast POP! series. These figures come in die-cast acrylic cases featuring etched details and fasten to the base of the case. The case can be opened, and the figure detached from the base, but with a clear view of all sides of your collectible, you won’t need to unbox it to see all the details. These collectibles come in a telescoping box that features foil details and a foam inner lining to further protect the collectible while in transit.

Continue your Die-cast POP! collection with POP! Tanjiro Kamado! Bring this exclusive member of the Demon Slayer Corps home to complete your Demon Slayer collection. There’s a 1 in 6 chance you might find the silver metallic chase variant.

Die-cast figure is approximately 4.3 in (10.9 cm) tall. Approximate case dimensions 4.5 in W x 6.3 in H x 3.5 in D (11.4 cm W x 16 cm H x 8.9 cm D).

Count down to your favorite festive holiday—or any special occasion—with the Disney Princess 24-Day Bitty POP! Countdown Calendar! Open the tiny doors to reveal 10 Bitty POP! collectibles, 9 stackable display pieces, 3 holiday accessories, 1 keychain case, and 1 pin case. Expand your princess lineup by making this Disney Princess 24-Day Bitty POP! Countdown Calendar the next addition to your collection. 

Bitty POP! collectibles are packaged in hard acrylic cases with detachable bottom lids. Detachable bottom lids double as acrylic bases, to which the Bitty POP! collectibles are adhered. Vinyl collectibles are approximately 0.9 in (2.3 cm) tall. Acrylic keychain cases and acrylic pin cases are approximately 1.3 in W x 1.6 in H x 1.2 in D (3.3 cm W x 4.1 cm H x 3 cm D) and fit all standard Bitty POP! cases. Bitty POP! Keychain is approximately 3 in (7.6 cm) long.

Warning: Choking Hazard. Collectibles are small. Not for children under the age of 3 years old.

Name: Jin Sakai
Description:
Step back in time to feudal Japan with the captivating Jin Sakai, immortalized in his dynamic stance as a Funko POP! Figure #621. This iconic collectible from the Ghost of Tsushima franchise brings to life the brave and honorable samurai warrior, ready to defend Tsushima from invaders. Fans of the critically acclaimed video game will appreciate the attention to detail, from Jin's traditional armor to his determined expression, making this POP! a must-have addition to any gaming collection.

Standing at the standard Funko POP! size, Jin Sakai radiates strength and determination as he carries his katana, embodying the essence of the Ghost of Tsushima world. The release of this figure in 2020 not only celebrates the game's success but also pays homage to the captivating journey players experienced alongside Jin. With his intricate armor and iconic pose, this POP! Figure captures the essence of Jin Sakai's character, making it a valuable and visually striking piece for any Funko collector or Ghost of Tsushima enthusiast.

Name: Jumbo Chan Astro Boy
Description:
Official Marketing Text:

Born of Funko’s reverence and passion for retro Japanese toys, Jumbo Chan is designed to emulate the charm and vibrance of iconic characters that have inspired so many of our artists. The Jumbo Chan collection merges feel-good nostalgia and sleek stylization of beloved licenses from the ‘60s through the ‘80s.

The Jumbo Chan Astro Boy collectible depicts the robot boy superhero, much like what fans saw in the original, early-1960s animated television series. The packaging is designed to emulate the packaging of the early action figures and features stylized front-panel art.

Astro Boy is the sixth edition of the collection. Astro Boy, a classic robot superhero that helped transform television storytelling in the 1960s, can live on now as a Jumbo Chan Astro Boy vinyl figure in your collection.

Name: Pan Am
Description:
Official Marketing Text

This edition of Project Fred features Freddy Funko personifying the Pan Am brand. This 11-inch-tall collectible is a substantial and sophisticated addition to a premium collector’s display. There’s a 1 in 10 chance you’ll find the chase version of Freddy in an alternate color palette design featuring the Pan Am logos and branding. Only 750 of this hard vinyl collectible were made, verified with a certificate of authenticity, making it a cherished addition to your set. Now it’s your chance to bring together your collection with the Pan Am Edition of Project Fred figure.

Whether you’re a collector of classic Ad Icon designs or a curator of more modern materials, Project Fred is the perfect collectible to pair with your set. It’s a great piece for an airline-themed set or as a statement piece to stand alongside iconic advertising collectibles. Own a piece of true Americana with the Pan Am Edition of Project Fred hard vinyl figure.

-Will you be lucky enough to win a chase variant from the launch? There’s a 1 in 10 chance you’ll unwrap an alternate deco chase.

-Sleek and eye-catching designs for ad icon collections. The display ideas are only limited by your creativity with Project Fred.

-Available only through this launch, never to be re-released.

-Only 750 of each made, making these 11-inch-tall, hard vinyl figures exclusive and sturdy additions to your collection.

Name: Michael Jordan
Description:
Official Marketing Text:

Behold! The new premiere POP! figure, designed to be the front and center, top-shelf collectible, the Die-cast POP! series. These figures come in die-cast acrylic cases featuring etched details and fasten to the base of the case. The case can be opened, and the figure detached from the base, but with a clear view of all sides of your collectible, you won't need to unbox it to see all the details. These collectibles come in a telescoping box that features foil details and a foam inner lining to further protect the collectible while in transit. Continue your Die-cast POP! collection with POP! Michael Jordan of the Chicago Bulls! Bring this exclusive basketball star home to complete your NBA collection. There's a 1 in 6 chance you might find the silver metallic chase variant. Die-cast figure is approximately 3.6 in (9.1 cm) tall.
